channel.description:
Alot of people have been having problems with adding this so I'll be showing you how to add this Welcome screen to a [PI] Server.

Okay lets go into how to add it to your server

Server sided, open up your Client.java

Search for public void initialize() {

Add this code underneath it:

[code=java]		getPA().showInterface(15244); //seankroes
		getPA().sendFrame126("@bla@Welcome to ServerName!", 15257);
		getPA().sendFrame126("Owner: OwnerName - Created by: seankroes - Last connected from: "+ connectedFrom, 15258);
		getPA().sendFrame126("Version 1.0 is now out! \\nDownload it now on URL.\\nVersion 2.0 will be out soon!", 15259); 
		getPA().sendFrame126("Useful commands\\n \\nRules - ::rules\\nCommands list - ::commands\\nStaff online - ::staff", 15260); 
		getPA().sendFrame126("", 15261);
		if(playerRights == 4) {
			getPA().sendFrame126("You're currently a member! \\nEnjoy the server with all features!\\n\\nYour membership NEVER expires!", 15262);
		} else {
			getPA().sendFrame126("You're currently not a member! \\nWe suggest you become one since it\\nHas huge benefits!\\nIt's only 5.00 euro's!", 15262);
		}
		getPA().sendFrame126("Play ServerName", 15263);
		getPA().sendFrame126("At 7 donators the server will be 24/7!\\nyou can also donate for rares!", 15270);[/code]

\\n = a new line of text.

